      out.write("                <div class=\"faq-answer hidden p-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed\">\r\n");
      out.write("                    The currency used in Morocco is the Moroccan dirham (MAD). It's advisable \r\n");
      out.write("                    to exchange currency upon arrival or use ATMs in major cities. Credit cards \r\n");
      out.write("                    are widely accepted in urban areas, but it's wise to carry some cash, \r\n");
      out.write("                    especially in rural locations. Keep in mind that some smaller establishments \r\n");
      out.write("                    may only accept cash. Check the current exchange rates and be aware of any \r\n");
